ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.message

Class RSP_Z82

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.message.RSP_Z82
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RSP_Z82
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a RSP_Z82 message structure (see chapter 5.9.1.1.1). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: UAC (User Authentication Credential Segment) optional
    • 4: MSA (Message Acknowledgment)
    • 5: ERR (Error) optional
    • 6: QAK (Query Acknowledgment)
    • 7: QPD (Query Parameter Definition)
    • 8: RCP (Response Control Parameter)
    • 9: RSP_Z82_QUERY_RESPONSE (a Group object) repeating
    • 10: DSC (Continuation Pointer) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
